Cám ơn về tách café.

175
00:23:16,386 --> 00:23:17,683
Sarah?

176
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:34,700
Sarah?

177
00:23:36,201 --> 00:23:38,101
Sarah...

178
00:24:06,309 --> 00:24:07,909
Sarah?

179
00:24:12,237 --> 00:24:14,204
Sarah?

180
00:25:04,574 --> 00:25:06,746
